  <summary date="2020-03-27T14:15:47Z" status="Introduced in House">Leave No Americans Behind Act of 2020

This bill eliminates the loan repatriation program, which requires persons who need to be evacuated from foreign countries during situations such as war or natural disasters to reimburse the U.S. government for certain evacuation costs.</summary>
